  "title": "Fear Fables: The Horror Drag Anthology",
  "description": "Prepare yourselves for a collection of terrifying tales... Fear Fables is where theatre, drag, and horror meet, in a way you've never seen before. In 2025, FF takes a galactic spin as we search the universe alongside narrator Emmonia, to unravel the cosmos' most horrifying legends through performance art, dance, and costume.",
  "credits": "<strong>Director</strong>: Mørtis X &amp; Emmonia<br><strong>Cast</strong>: Emmonia, Mørtis X, Art Official, CallMeKeeks, Damien Ghoul, Jizz Elle, Mx Jackson, Romulus<br/></br>",
  "website": "https://instagram.com/epo.artsco",
  "plain_language": "\"Fear Fables: The Horror Drag Anthology\" is a 60-minute drag show where each number tells a different horror story. This show is narrated/hosted by Emmonia, a local drag icon, who plays an ancient demon that feeds on terror to survive. Follow her as she navigates the galaxy collecting horror legends for her Fear Fables book, the collection of horror stories where she holds all of her demonic power.",
